<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Rapport d'Optimisation AEP V11 - {{ metadata.method|default('M√©thode') }}</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary-color: #2c3e50;
            --secondary-color: #3498db;
            --accent-color: #e74c3c;
            --success-color: #27ae60;
            --warning-color: #f39c12;
            --text-color: #2c3e50;
            --light-gray: #ecf0f1;
            --border-color: #bdc3c7;
        }
        
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: var(--text-color);
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: white;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 30px 0;
            border-bottom: 3px solid var(--primary-color);
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        
        .header h1 {
            color: var(--primary-color);
            font-size: 2.5em;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .header h2 {
            color: var(--secondary-color);
            font-size: 1.5em;
            font-weight: 300;
        }
        
        .metadata-section {
            background-color: var(--light-gray);
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        
        .metadata-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
            gap: 15px;
        }
        
        .metadata-item {
            background-color: white;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            border-left: 4px solid var(--secondary-color);
        }
        
        .metadata-item strong {
            color: var(--primary-color);
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        
        .optimization-summary {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-color), var(--secondary-color));
            color: white;
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .summary-stats {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        
        .stat-item {
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .stat-value {
            font-size: 2em;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        
        .stat-label {
            font-size: 0.9em;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
        
        .proposals-section {
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }
        
        .section-title {
            color: var(--primary-color);
            font-size: 1.8em;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--secondary-color);
        }
        
        .proposal-card {
            background-color: white;
            border: 2px solid var(--light-gray);
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .proposal-card:hover {
            border-color: var(--secondary-color);
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        
        .proposal-header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            padding-bottom: 15px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--light-gray);
        }
        
        .proposal-name {
            font-size: 1.4em;
            color: var(--primary-color);
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        
        .feasibility-badge {
            padding: 5px 15px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 0.9em;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        
        .feasible {
            background-color: var(--success-color);
            color: white;
        }
        
        .infeasible {
            background-color: var(--accent-color);
            color: white;
        }
        
        .proposal-details {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
        }
        
        .detail-group {
            background-color: var(--light-gray);
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 6px;
        }
        
        .detail-group h4 {
            color: var(--primary-color);
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-size: 1.1em;
        }
        
        .detail-item {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            padding: 5px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        
        .detail-item:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        
        .detail-label {
            font-weight: 500;
            color: var(--text-color);
        }
        
        .detail-value {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: var(--secondary-color);
        }
        
        .costs-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
        
        .costs-table th,
        .costs-table td {
            padding: 8px 12px;
            text-align: left;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);
        }
        
        .costs-table th {
            background-color: var(--primary-color);
            color: white;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        
        .costs-table tr:nth-child(even) {
            background-color: var(--light-gray);
        }
        
        .pareto-section {
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }
        
        .pareto-chart {
            background-color: var(--light-gray);
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            text-align: center;
            min-height: 200px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }
        
        .pareto-placeholder {
            color: var(--text-color);
            font-style: italic;
        }
        
        .recommendations {
            background-color: #e8f4fd;
            border: 2px solid var(--secondary-color);
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 25px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        
        .recommendations h3 {
            color: var(--primary-color);
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 1.5em;
        }
        
        .recommendation-item {
            background-color: white;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            border-left: 4px solid var(--secondary-color);
        }
        
        .recommendation-item:last-child {
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }
        
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            color: var(--text-color);
            border-top: 1px solid var(--light-gray);
            margin-top: 30px;
        }
        
        .footer p {
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        
        .lcpi-brand {
            color: var(--secondary-color);
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .container {
                margin: 10px;
                padding: 15px;
            }
            
            .header h1 {
                font-size: 2em;
            }
            
            .metadata-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
            
            .proposal-details {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
            
            .summary-stats {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <!-- En-t√™te du rapport -->
        <div class="header">
            <h1>üìä Rapport d'Optimisation AEP</h1>
            <h2>Version V11 - {{ metadata.method|default('M√©thode d\'optimisation') }}</h2>
        </div>
        
        <!-- M√©tadonn√©es du projet -->
        <div class="metadata-section">
            <h3 class="section-title">üìã Informations du Projet</h3>
            <div class="metadata-grid">
                <div class="metadata-item">
                    <strong>M√©thode d'optimisation</strong>
                    <span>{{ metadata.method|default('Non sp√©cifi√©') }}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="metadata-item">
                    <strong>Fichier r√©seau</strong>
                    <span>{{ metadata.network_file|default('Non sp√©cifi√©') }}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="metadata-item">
                    <strong>Date de g√©n√©ration</strong>
                    <span>{{ now.strftime('%d/%m/%Y √† %H:%M') if now else 'Non sp√©cifi√©' }}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="metadata-item">
                    <strong>Version LCPI</strong>
                    <span>V11</span>
                </div>
                {% if metadata.algorithm %}
                <div class="metadata-item">
                    <strong>Algorithme</strong>
                    <span>{{ metadata.algorithm }}</span>
                </div>
                {% endif %}
                {% if metadata.iterations %}
                <div class="metadata-item">
                    <strong>It√©rations</strong>
                    <span>{{ metadata.iterations }}</span>
                </div>
                {% endif %}
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- R√©sum√© de l'optimisation -->
        <div class="optimization-summary">
            <h3>üéØ R√©sum√© de l'Optimisation</h3>
            <div class="summary-stats">
                <div class="stat-item">
                    <div class="stat-value">{{ proposals|length }}</div>
                    <div class="stat-label">Propositions</div>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-item">
                    <div class="stat-value">{{ proposals|selectattr('is_feasible')|list|length }}</div>
                    <div class="stat-label">Solutions Faisables</div>
                </div>
                {% if pareto_front %}
                <div class="stat-item">
                    <div class="stat-value">{{ pareto_front|length }}</div>
                    <div class="stat-label">Points Pareto</div>
                </div>
                {% endif %}
                {% if metadata.execution_time %}
                <div class="stat-item">
                    <div class="stat-value">{{ metadata.execution_time }}</div>
                    <div class="stat-label">Temps d'ex√©cution</div>
                </div>
                {% endif %}
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Propositions d'optimisation -->
        <div class="proposals-section">
            <h3 class="section-title">üèóÔ∏è Propositions d'Optimisation</h3>
            
            {% for proposal in proposals %}
            <div class="proposal-card">
                <div class="proposal-header">
                    <div class="proposal-name">{{ proposal.name }}</div>
                    <div class="feasibility-badge {{ 'feasible' if proposal.is_feasible else 'infeasible' }}">
                        {{ '‚úÖ Faisable' if proposal.is_feasible else '‚ùå Non faisable' }}
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="proposal-details">
                    <!-- R√©servoirs -->
                    {% if proposal.tanks %}
                    <div class="detail-group">
                        <h4>üè∫ R√©servoirs</h4>
                        {% for tank in proposal.tanks %}
                        <div class="detail-item">
                            <span class="detail-label">{{ tank.id }}</span>
                            <span class="detail-value">{{ "%.2f"|format(tank.H_m) }} m</span>
                        </div>
                        {% endfor %}
                    </div>
                    {% endif %}
                    
                    <!-- Diam√®tres -->
                    {% if proposal.diameters_mm %}
                    <div class="detail-group">
                        <h4>üîß Diam√®tres des Conduites</h4>
                        {% for pipe, diameter in proposal.diameters_mm.items() %}
                        <div class="detail-item">
                            <span class="detail-label">{{ pipe }}</span>
                            <span class="detail-value">{{ diameter }} mm</span>
                        </div>
                        {% endfor %}
                    </div>
                    {% endif %}
                    
                    <!-- Co√ªts -->
                    {% if proposal.costs %}
                    <div class="detail-group">
                        <h4>üí∞ Analyse des Co√ªts</h4>
                        <table class="costs-table">
                            <thead>
                                <tr>
                                    <th>Type de co√ªt</th>
                                    <th>Montant (FCFA)</th>
                                </tr>
                            </thead>
                            <tbody>
                                {% if proposal.costs.CAPEX %}
                                <tr>
                                    <td>CAPEX (Investissement)</td>
                                    <td>{{ "{:,.0f}".format(proposal.costs.CAPEX) }}</td>
                                </tr>
                                {% endif %}
                                {% if proposal.costs.OPEX_annual %}
                                <tr>
                                    <td>OPEX Annuel</td>
                                    <td>{{ "{:,.0f}".format(proposal.costs.OPEX_annual) }}</td>
                                </tr>
                                {% endif %}
                                {% if proposal.costs.OPEX_npv %}
                                <tr>
                                    <td>OPEX NPV (20 ans)</td>
                                    <td>{{ "{:,.0f}".format(proposal.costs.OPEX_npv) }}</td>
                                </tr>
                                {% endif %}
                                {% if proposal.costs.total %}
                                <tr>
                                    <td><strong>Co√ªt Total</strong></td>
                                    <td><strong>{{ "{:,.0f}".format(proposal.costs.total) }}</strong></td>
                                </tr>
                                {% endif %}
                            </tbody>
                        </table>
                    </div>
                    {% endif %}
                    
                    <!-- M√©triques -->
                    {% if proposal.metrics %}
                    <div class="detail-group">
                        <h4>üìä M√©triques de Performance</h4>
                        {% for metric, value in proposal.metrics.items() %}
                        {% if value is not none %}
                        <div class="detail-item">
                            <span class="detail-label">
                                {% if metric == 'min_pressure_m' %}Pression minimale
                                {% elif metric == 'max_velocity_m_s' %}Vitesse maximale
                                {% elif metric == 'iterations' %}It√©rations
                                {% else %}{{ metric }}{% endif %}
                            </span>
                            <span class="detail-value">
                                {% if metric == 'min_pressure_m' %}{{ "%.2f"|format(value) }} m
                                {% elif metric == 'max_velocity_m_s' %}{{ "%.2f"|format(value) }} m/s
                                {% else %}{{ value }}{% endif %}
                            </span>
                        </div>
                        {% endif %}
                        {% endfor %}
                    </div>
                    {% endif %}
                </div>
            </div>
            {% endfor %}
        </div>
        
        <!-- Front de Pareto -->
        {% if pareto_front %}
        <div class="pareto-section">
            <h3 class="section-title">üìà Front de Pareto</h3>
            <div class="pareto-chart">
                <div class="pareto-placeholder">
                    <h4>üéØ Solutions Pareto Optimales</h4>
                    <p>Nombre de solutions : {{ pareto_front|length }}</p>
                    <p>Visualisation graphique √† impl√©menter</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        {% endif %}
        
        <!-- Recommandations -->
        <div class="recommendations">
            <h3>üí° Recommandations</h3>
            
            {% if proposals|selectattr('is_feasible')|list|length > 0 %}
            <div class="recommendation-item">
                <strong>‚úÖ Solutions recommand√©es :</strong> 
                {{ proposals|selectattr('is_feasible')|list|length }} solution(s) faisable(s) identifi√©e(s).
                {% if proposals|selectattr('is_feasible')|list|length == 1 %}
                Cette solution unique est recommand√©e pour l'impl√©mentation.
                {% else %}
                Comparez les solutions selon vos crit√®res de priorit√© (co√ªt, performance, etc.).
                {% endif %}
            </div>
            
            {% set best_capex = proposals|selectattr('is_feasible')|sort(attribute='costs.CAPEX')|first %}
            {% if best_capex %}
            <div class="recommendation-item">
                <strong>üí∞ Solution la moins ch√®re :</strong> 
                {{ best_capex.name }} avec un CAPEX de {{ "{:,.0f}".format(best_capex.costs.CAPEX) }} FCFA.
            </div>
            {% endif %}
            
            {% set best_pressure = proposals|selectattr('is_feasible')|sort(attribute='metrics.min_pressure_m', reverse=true)|first %}
            {% if best_pressure %}
            <div class="recommendation-item">
                <strong>üîß Solution la plus robuste :</strong> 
                {{ best_pressure.name }} avec une pression minimale de {{ "%.2f"|format(best_pressure.metrics.min_pressure_m) }} m.
            </div>
            {% endif %}
            
            {% else %}
            <div class="recommendation-item">
                <strong>‚ö†Ô∏è Aucune solution faisable :</strong> 
                Aucune des solutions g√©n√©r√©es ne respecte les contraintes. 
                V√©rifiez les param√®tres d'optimisation et les contraintes du r√©seau.
            </div>
            {% endif %}
            
            <div class="recommendation-item">
                <strong>üìã Prochaines √©tapes :</strong> 
                Validez les solutions recommand√©es par une simulation d√©taill√©e, 
                puis proc√©dez √† la conception d√©taill√©e et √† la planification de l'ex√©cution.
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Pied de page -->
        <div class="footer">
            <p><span class="lcpi-brand">LCPI</span> - Logiciel de Calcul et Planification d'Infrastructure</p>
            <p>Rapport g√©n√©r√© le {{ now.strftime('%d/%m/%Y √† %H:%M:%S') if now else 'Date non disponible' }}</p>
            <p>Version V11 - Format d'optimisation AEP</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
